# Cloudflare Pages headers for admin-studio-ui.
#
# Google Sign-In opens an OAuth popup and posts the credential back via
# window.postMessage. A strict Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy severs that
# popup<->opener channel ("COOP policy would block the window.postMessage
# call"). `same-origin-allow-popups` keeps cross-origin isolation for the
# document while still allowing our own popups to talk back.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin-allow-popups
